-- Apple’s Smaller IPad to Double 7-Inch Tablet Market, IHS Says
-- B y   L i s a   R a p a p o r t
-- 2012-10-23T13:16:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-23/apple-s-smaller-ipad-to-double-7-inch-tablet-market-ihs-says.html
Apple Inc. (AAPL) ’s smaller iPad, which the
company is expected to debut today, will help double the size of
the market for 7-inch tablets this year, according to IHS
ISuppli.  Global sales of tablets with 7-inch displays will surge to
about 34 million units this year, from 17 million last year, IHS
said in a report today. Next year, the market will nearly double 
again, to about 67 million units.  To contact the reporter on this story:
